### Calculator MCP Tool - HTTP Requests
### Tests the MCP tool that calls the Calculator A2A agent
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7077

### Get Calculator Agent Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Calculate - Simple Addition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expression": "5 + 3"
}

###

